Crow's Nest Environmental is an environmental consulting firm, with its office located in Corbyville, Ontario about one hour east of Toronto.  Crow's Nest Environmental specializes in:
Sustainability Materials Management with in the Circular Economy;
Environmental policy development and evaluation;
Packaging design optimization for recycling;
Extended Producer Responsibility (EPR) policy planning and program development;
Material Recovery Facility operations and optimization;
Recycling program design;
Recycling Request for Proposals (RFP) preparation and administration;
Recycling contract design and administration; and
Environmental policy development.

Over more than 30 years, clients have included all levels of government in Canada, state governments in the United States, private and public corporations, industry associations, and stewardship agencies.

We welcome you to explore our website and contact us if you have any questions. 

And yes, all of the photos on this site were taken at The Crow's Nest property in Corbyville, Ontario.
